| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Step | Actor | Action | System Response |
| 1 | User | Request hot path analysis | Validate call graph exists |
| 2 | System | Calculate in-degree for all nodes | Count callers per function |
| 3 | System | Calculate betweenness centrality | Find nodes on many shortest paths |
| 4 | System | Identify hub nodes (high in + out degree) | Flag as architectural hotspots |
| 5 | System | Rank by composite score | Return top-N results |

#### API Contract

**Request:**

{
